 {u'keywords': [u'小米', u'镜头'], u'data': u'在央视看来，双 11 虽然绝大多数情况下都是淘宝唱主角，但是也有京东、小米和其他方加入，尤其是京东的镜头在里面出现了好几次。希望以此来做到总体上的公平和客观。', u'type': u'text'}, {u'data': {u'small': {u'url': u'http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=6d0bb482f5deb48ffb69a2ddc81d3aef/b03533fa828ba61e3822e6cc4734970a314e5900.jpg&fm=37', u'width': 480, u'height': 270}, u'big': {u'url': u'http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=6d0bb482f5deb48ffb69a2ddc81d3aef/b03533fa828ba61e3822e6cc4734970a314e5900.jpg&fm=38', u'width': 638, u'height': 359}, u'original': {u'url': u'http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=6d0bb482f5deb48ffb69a2ddc81d3aef/b03533fa828ba61e3822e6cc4734970a314e5900.jpg', u'width': 638, u'height': 359}, u'original_third': {u'url': u'http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=6d0bb482f5deb48ffb69a2ddc81d3aef/b03533fa828ba61e3822e6cc4734970a314e5900.jpg', u'width': 638, u'height': 359}}, u'type': u'image'}, {u'data': {u'small': {u'url': u'http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=http://f.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=2a1ed5c89b16fdfad86cc5ed8c8d8cea/810a19d8bc3eb135be0b9958a01ea8d3fc1f4400.jpg&fm=37', u'width': 480, u'height': 270}, u'big': {u'url': u'http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=http://f.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=2a1ed5c89b16fdfad86cc5ed8c8d8cea/810a19d8bc3eb135be0b9958a01ea8d3fc1f4400.jpg&fm=38', u'width': 638, u'height': 359}, u'original': {u'url': u'http://f.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=2a1ed5c89b16fdfad86cc5ed8c8d8cea/810a19d8bc3eb135be0b9958a01ea8d3fc1f4400.jpg', u'width': 638, u'height': 359}, u'original_third': {u'url': u'http://f.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=2a1ed5c89b16fdfad86cc5ed8c8d8cea/810a19d8bc3eb135be0b9958a01ea8d3fc1f4400.jpg', u'width': 638, u'height': 359}}, u'type': u'image'}, {u'keywords': [u'小米'], u'data': u'而这里是小米。', u'type': u'text'}, {u'data': u'采访对象有：', u'type': u'text'}, {u'data': {u'small': {u'url': u'http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/news/w%3D638/sign=4ba18c